<font color="yellow">You have a big sister?</font>

217
00:28:39,370 --> 00:28:41,240
<font color="yellow">Have you seen my little sister?</font>

218
00:28:42,000 --> 00:28:43,840
<font color="yellow">Think about it. Where was it?</font>

219
00:28:44,940 --> 00:28:46,000
<font color="yellow">Little sister...</font>

220
00:28:47,200 --> 00:28:49,700
<font color="yellow">I think she may be one of my deceased souls,</font>

221
00:28:49,870 --> 00:28:51,500
<font color="yellow">but I'm not positive.</font>

222
00:28:51,770 --> 00:28:53,840
<font color="yellow">She was reincarnated? When?</font>

223
00:28:53,840 --> 00:28:55,240
<font color="yellow">I said I wasn't sure.</font>

224
00:28:55,670 --> 00:28:59,070
<font color="yellow">I can't remember everyone I took away.</font>

225
00:29:00,800 --> 00:29:04,440
<font color="yellow">She seems familiar, so I'm guessing.</font>

226
00:29:06,200 --> 00:29:09,340
<font color="yellow">I don't remember. I just feel.</font>

227
00:29:11,070 --> 00:29:13,240
<font color="yellow">I was just extremely sad.</font>

228
00:29:14,970 --> 00:29:16,900
<font color="yellow">My heart felt like it was breaking.</font>

229
00:29:17,940 --> 00:29:20,600
<font color="yellow">Uncles, I know.</font>

230
00:29:21,270 --> 00:29:22,440
<font color="yellow">I think I know.</font>

231
00:29:23,640 --> 00:29:26,270
<font color="yellow">Maybe the Grim Reaper is your sister's reincarnation.</font>

232
00:29:26,270 --> 00:29:27,770
<font color="yellow">Try calling him your brother.</font>

233
00:29:27,770 --> 00:29:29,270
<font color="yellow">- Do you want to die? - Do you want to die?</font>

234
00:29:41,670 --> 00:29:42,700
<font color="yellow">Bro...</font>

235
00:29:47,100 --> 00:29:48,200
<font color="yellow">Broth...</font>

236
00:29:51,100 --> 00:29:53,740
<font color="yellow">Have you heard the news?</font>

237
00:29:54,400 --> 00:29:55,970
<font color="yellow">About Messenger Kim from Janghang-dong.</font>

238
00:29:55,970 --> 00:29:57,900
<font color="yellow">What about him?</font>

239
00:29:57,900 --> 00:29:59,770
<font color="yellow">He went to pick up a soul,</font>

240
00:29:59,970 --> 00:30:02,600
<font color="yellow">and it was his wife in a previous life.</font>

241
00:30:02,640 --> 00:30:06,440
<font color="yellow">So he put her name on the missing soul's list and ran off with her.</font>

242
00:30:07,640 --> 00:30:09,700
<font color="yellow">- So? - That is all.</font>

243
00:30:10,040 --> 00:30:11,400
<font color="yellow">I don't know the rest.</font>

244
00:30:11,970 --> 00:30:13,770
<font color="yellow">I'm sure they were caught.</font>

245
00:30:13,770 --> 00:30:16,200
<font color="yellow">How did he remember his past life?</font>

246
00:30:16,200 --> 00:30:17,370
<font color="yellow">Who knows?</font>

247
00:30:18,270 --> 00:30:22,070
<font color="yellow">That's why everyone's nervous. I've been drinking every day, too.</font>

248
00:30:22,270 --> 00:30:23,940
<font color="yellow">I keep thinking.</font>

249
00:30:24,240 --> 00:30:27,500
<font color="yellow">They say you become a grim reaper if you commit a great sin.</font>

250
00:30:28,100 --> 00:30:30,670
<font color="yellow">I wonder how bad a sin it was.</font>

251
00:30:31,040 --> 00:30:33,700
<font color="yellow">Maybe they erased our memory so that we wouldn't be tormented by it.</font>

252
00:30:34,100 --> 00:30:36,170
<font color="yellow">So that we can repent while doing this work?</font>

253
00:30:37,100 --> 00:30:38,370
<font color="yellow">It must be the deity's consideration.</font>

254
00:30:38,470 --> 00:30:42,440
<font color="yellow">If you remember, you remember. If not, you don't.</font>

255
00:30:42,840 --> 00:30:44,270
<font color="yellow">It is all the deity's will.</font>

256
00:30:44,470 --> 00:30:47,600
<font color="yellow">However, I wonder why he returned the memories...</font>

257
00:30:48,040 --> 00:30:50,500
<font color="yellow">that he had forgotten.</font>

258
00:30:52,670 --> 00:30:53,800
<font color="yellow">I wonder.</font>

259
00:30:58,170 --> 00:30:59,670
<font color="yellow">Jin Young!</font>

260
00:31:01,570 --> 00:31:03,200
<font color="yellow">Let's go.</font>

261
00:31:03,940 --> 00:31:05,470
<font color="yellow">- Did you have fun? - Yes.</font>

262
00:31:05,870 --> 00:31:07,370
<font color="yellow">What should we eat?</font>

263
00:31:13,000 --> 00:31:14,240
<font color="yellow">I need to go.</font>

264
00:31:17,770 --> 00:31:19,440
<font color="yellow">Don't drink too much.</font>

265
00:31:23,070 --> 00:31:24,200
<font color="yellow">Have a nice day.</font>

266
00:31:34,500 --> 00:31:37,040
<font color="yellow">Mom, where are we?</font>

267
00:31:38,700 --> 00:31:40,600
<font color="yellow">I think it's a tea shop.</font>

268
00:31:41,940 --> 00:31:45,400
<font color="yellow">What are we drinking? What are you going to order?</font>

269
00:31:45,540 --> 00:31:49,340
<font color="yellow">I ordered paradise...</font>

270
00:31:49,870 --> 00:31:51,840
<font color="yellow">to give it to you.</font>

271
00:31:54,640 --> 00:31:55,970
<font color="yellow">Paradise?</font>

272
00:32:07,570 --> 00:32:10,470
<font color="yellow">Here is paradise that you ordered.</font>

273
00:32:12,270 --> 00:32:13,570
<font color="yellow">Thank you.</font>

274
00:32:13,740 --> 00:32:16,470
<font color="yellow">Mom, why are you crying?</font>

275
00:32:48,470 --> 00:32:50,440
<font color="yellow">- What are you doing? - Oh my gosh.</font>

276
00:32:51,870 --> 00:32:53,570
<font color="yellow">What are you doing there?</font>

277
00:32:54,640 --> 00:32:56,340
<font color="yellow">I was going to the library.</font>

278
00:32:56,470 --> 00:32:58,470
<font color="yellow">What about you? Do you know them?</font>

279
00:33:01,500 --> 00:33:03,070
<font color="yellow">Who are you?</font>

280
00:33:03,070 --> 00:33:04,270
<font color="yellow">Step aside.</font>

281
00:33:12,640 --> 00:33:16,340
<font color="yellow">Open the window, air out the room, and button up.</font>

282
00:33:18,640 --> 00:33:19,770
<font color="yellow">You'll need this.</font>

283
00:33:23,600 --> 00:33:24,700
<font color="yellow">Let's go.</font>

284
00:33:40,940 --> 00:33:42,900
<font color="yellow">Daddy.</font>

285
00:33:46,570 --> 00:33:48,970
<font color="yellow">Hi. How did you get here?</font>

286
00:33:48,970 --> 00:33:51,200
<font color="yellow">I got in a taxi and showed her the address.</font>

287
00:33:51,200 --> 00:33:53,370
<font color="yellow">It was five dollars.</font>

288
00:33:55,200 --> 00:33:57,840
<font color="yellow">- I'm going here. - I know where that is.</font>

289
00:33:58,540 --> 00:33:59,770
<font color="yellow">Buckle up.</font>

290
00:33:59,770 --> 00:34:02,000
<font color="yellow">Daddy, I'm hungry.</font>

291
00:34:02,370 --> 00:34:03,540
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

292
00:34:03,970 --> 00:34:06,400
<font color="yellow">Okay. Here.</font>

293
00:34:07,840 --> 00:34:10,170
<font color="yellow">Daddy, I've missed you.</font>

294
00:34:13,700 --> 00:34:14,840
<font color="yellow">Me too.</font>

295
00:34:25,670 --> 00:34:28,670
<font color="yellow">You were pretty cool again today.</font>

296
00:34:31,900 --> 00:34:34,700
<font color="yellow">At times, a parent, a child, or a sibling...</font>

297
00:34:35,240 --> 00:34:37,900
<font color="yellow">becomes each other's guardian spirit.</font>

298
00:34:38,570 --> 00:34:40,870
<font color="yellow">I merely gave him a sandwich.</font>

299
00:34:42,040 --> 00:34:44,740
<font color="yellow">I did not save that man. His daughter did.</font>

300
00:34:47,770 --> 00:34:49,340
<font color="yellow">That's cool too.</font>

301
00:34:50,200 --> 00:34:52,070
<font color="yellow">The sandwich costs a lot.</font>

302
00:34:52,270 --> 00:34:54,140
<font color="yellow">It's a good thing Chairman Yu makes a lot of money.</font>

303
00:34:56,170 --> 00:34:59,170
<font color="yellow">But you know, about the sword...</font>

304
00:35:00,470 --> 00:35:02,610
<font color="yellow">Why do you think it suddenly moved?</font>

305
00:35:02,840 --> 00:35:05,140
<font color="yellow">I couldn't even grab it. Right?</font>

306
00:35:06,140 --> 00:35:09,340
<font color="yellow">Maybe you need something more powerful than a curse.</font>

307
00:35:09,440 --> 00:35:13,940
<font color="yellow">For example, true love. Something like that.</font>

308
00:35:15,140 --> 00:35:17,800
<font color="yellow">Don't you have something to say to me?</font>

309
00:35:18,740 --> 00:35:20,500
<font color="yellow">- No, I don't. - I'm sure you do.</font>

310
00:35:23,970 --> 00:35:25,270
<font color="yellow">Oh, that?</font>

311
00:35:25,270 --> 00:35:27,770
<font color="yellow">- There is one thing. - See? You do.</font>

312
00:35:27,770 --> 00:35:29,570
<font color="yellow">Don't hold it in. You're totally obvious.</font>

313
00:35:29,570 --> 00:35:30,970
<font color="yellow">Tell me. It's okay.</font>

314
00:35:31,270 --> 00:35:34,610
<font color="yellow">Whatever you say, I'll accept it without judgment.</font>

315
00:35:42,970 --> 00:35:45,640
<font color="yellow">I know you have a lot of money,</font>

316
00:35:47,270 --> 00:35:49,900
<font color="yellow">but is it okay to just stay home?</font>

317
00:35:52,270 --> 00:35:53,800
<font color="yellow">Is that what you wanted to tell me?</font>

318
00:35:53,800 --> 00:35:56,270
<font color="yellow">You worked for the country during the Goryeo Era, but that's it.</font>

319
00:35:56,270 --> 00:35:59,040
<font color="yellow">Hey. Are you done? I had a career, too.</font>

320
00:35:59,270 --> 00:36:03,570
<font color="yellow">It won't make you immortal, but you won't get drunk for a while.</font>

321
00:36:16,140 --> 00:36:20,070
<font color="yellow">It won't make you immortal, but you'll smell nice for a while.</font>

322
00:36:28,070 --> 00:36:31,670
<font color="yellow">It won't make you immortal, but you'll be happy for a while.</font>

323
00:36:32,240 --> 00:36:34,040
<font color="yellow">Why are you talking down to me?</font>

324
00:36:34,070 --> 00:36:35,400
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry, Ma'am.</font>

325
00:36:36,040 --> 00:36:37,800
<font color="yellow">- Yu Jae Shin. - My apologies.</font>

326
00:36:38,800 --> 00:36:40,000
<font color="yellow">My apologies for that, as well.</font>

327
00:36:40,270 --> 00:36:42,670
<font color="yellow">That's why you just stay home.</font>

328
00:36:42,870 --> 00:36:45,500
<font color="yellow">- Because you are lacking. - What do you mean, I'm lacking?</font>

329
00:36:45,500 --> 00:36:48,540
<font color="yellow">What do you think? You're lacking brain cells.</font>

330
00:36:48,640 --> 00:36:51,500
<font color="yellow">Seriously, I've never heard that before.</font>

331
00:36:51,500 --> 00:36:53,200
<font color="yellow">Ever. Seriously. Never.</font>

332
00:36:53,400 --> 00:36:56,940
<font color="yellow">I guess your first love never told you that.</font>

333
00:36:56,940 --> 00:36:58,500
<font color="yellow">Are you jealous?</font>

334
00:36:59,370 --> 00:37:02,270
<font color="yellow">What? Why would I be jealous?</font>

335
00:37:02,270 --> 00:37:05,070
<font color="yellow">I don't know when she lived or anything.</font>

336
00:37:05,070 --> 00:37:07,170
<font color="yellow">When did you meet? Goryeo? Joseon?</font>

337
00:37:07,170 --> 00:37:08,470
<font color="yellow">Mid Joseon? Late Joseon?</font>

338
00:37:08,470 --> 00:37:10,870
<font color="yellow">I'm sure she must have been pretty.</font>

339
00:37:11,040 --> 00:37:15,270
<font color="yellow">But you know, first loves never work out.</font>

340
00:37:19,770 --> 00:37:22,340
<font color="yellow">Go home. Don't wait for me.</font>

341
00:37:22,670 --> 00:37:24,070
<font color="yellow">I'll be late.</font>

342
00:37:34,740 --> 00:37:37,070
<font color="yellow">Who says first loves don't work out?</font>

343
00:37:39,270 --> 00:37:40,570
<font color="yellow">I don't like that.</font>

344
00:37:47,800 --> 00:37:49,640
<font color="yellow">- Hey. - Ho.</font>

345
00:37:50,670 --> 00:37:51,700
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

346
00:37:57,800 --> 00:37:59,200
<font color="yellow">What's "Hey, ho"?</font>

347
00:38:00,370 --> 00:38:03,470
<font color="yellow">Wasn't that funny? Everyone else thought it was funny.</font>

348
00:38:04,370 --> 00:38:05,440
<font color="yellow">It's lame.</font>

349
00:38:08,200 --> 00:38:11,670
<font color="yellow">You know, your birthmark faded a lot.</font>

350
00:38:14,500 --> 00:38:17,070
<font color="yellow">Really? Maybe it's because I'm getting older.</font>

351
00:38:23,900 --> 00:38:27,740
<font color="yellow">Why do you always waste money on this when I can't drink it?</font>

352
00:38:27,800 --> 00:38:29,070
<font color="yellow">It's such a waste.</font>

353
00:38:29,540 --> 00:38:32,070
<font color="yellow">Who would get you coffee other than me?</font>

354
00:38:32,970 --> 00:38:34,370
<font color="yellow">How did the exams go?</font>

355
00:38:34,770 --> 00:38:36,700
<font color="yellow">Good, of course.</font>

356
00:38:38,370 --> 00:38:40,870
<font color="yellow">That's why you should tell me your story before it's too late.</font>

357
00:38:53,940 --> 00:38:55,400
<font color="yellow">Other ghosts are busy...</font>

358
00:38:55,440 --> 00:38:58,370
<font color="yellow">telling me their stories and begging me to help them.</font>

359
00:38:58,870 --> 00:39:00,640
<font color="yellow">Why haven't you said anything to me?</font>

360
00:39:01,340 --> 00:39:04,310
<font color="yellow">Once I go to college, I won't be able to come here often.</font>

361
00:39:05,670 --> 00:39:06,770
<font color="yellow">Then...</font>

362
00:39:07,240 --> 00:39:09,100
<font color="yellow">will you come visit me?</font>

363
00:39:09,570 --> 00:39:11,100
<font color="yellow">I'd love some nice flowers.</font>

364
00:39:12,400 --> 00:39:14,170
<font color="yellow">I'm in Paju.</font>

365
00:39:16,640 --> 00:39:18,470
<font color="yellow">Okay. I'll come.</font>

366
00:39:21,240 --> 00:39:22,340
<font color="yellow">By the way,</font>

367
00:39:23,000 --> 00:39:25,570
<font color="yellow">how did you die?</font>

368
00:39:25,900 --> 00:39:27,570
<font color="yellow">It was on my graduation day.</font>

369
00:39:29,310 --> 00:39:30,570
<font color="yellow">There was a car accident.</font>

370
00:39:32,340 --> 00:39:33,870
<font color="yellow">I'll be waiting, then.</font>

371
00:39:50,310 --> 00:39:52,600
<font color="yellow">What happened to her?</font>

372
00:39:55,220 --> 00:39:56,820
<font color="yellow">- Welcome. - Hello.</font>

373
00:39:59,970 --> 00:40:02,370
<font color="yellow">How did you know I was here?</font>

374
00:40:04,470 --> 00:40:07,240
<font color="yellow">I'm even more surprised. Why did it have to be here?</font>

375
00:40:07,400 --> 00:40:09,400
<font color="yellow">There are more chicken restaurants in Korea than the total number...</font>

376
00:40:09,400 --> 00:40:11,370
<font color="yellow">of McDonald's in the world.</font>

377
00:40:11,370 --> 00:40:13,170
<font color="yellow">Why did it have to be this one?</font>

378
00:40:13,470 --> 00:40:15,900
<font color="yellow">Because this is the one Mr. Goblin put me in.</font>

379
00:40:16,210 --> 00:40:18,370
<font color="yellow">He's such a hindrance to my life.</font>

380
00:40:18,400 --> 00:40:19,970
<font color="yellow">What is it today?</font>

381
00:40:19,970 --> 00:40:23,900
<font color="yellow">You're giving me heart attacks. Are you going to keep this up?</font>

382
00:40:25,070 --> 00:40:26,540
<font color="yellow">Why do you think I'm here?</font>

383
00:40:26,540 --> 00:40:28,040
<font color="yellow">I'm here to get chicken. Give me one.</font>

384
00:40:28,040 --> 00:40:29,440
<font color="yellow">Don't lie.</font>

385
00:40:29,440 --> 00:40:31,570
<font color="yellow">I know you're a vegetarian.</font>

386
00:40:31,570 --> 00:40:33,240
<font color="yellow">Even if you know, give me one.</font>

387
00:40:33,970 --> 00:40:35,700
<font color="yellow">I want that one with extra radishes.</font>

388
00:40:37,000 --> 00:40:38,040
<font color="yellow">Really?</font>

389
00:40:45,370 --> 00:40:47,700
<font color="yellow">Were you supposed to meet him?</font>

390
00:40:47,970 --> 00:40:51,940
<font color="yellow">Did I just walk in at the scene by coincidence?</font>

391
00:40:56,870 --> 00:40:59,370
<font color="yellow">What are you doing? You can't touch that.</font>

392
00:40:59,370 --> 00:41:02,000
<font color="yellow">You're not supposed to be seen by humans, either.</font>

393
00:41:02,000 --> 00:41:03,870
<font color="yellow">Just go sit in the corner.</font>

394
00:41:03,870 --> 00:41:06,040
<font color="yellow">If you stay quiet, I'll give you an extra drumstick.</font>

395
00:41:08,770 --> 00:41:10,100
<font color="yellow">Welcome.</font>

396
00:41:10,640 --> 00:41:12,100
<font color="yellow">Have you been well?</font>

397
00:41:12,740 --> 00:41:14,140
<font color="yellow">Please take a seat.</font>

398
00:41:15,740 --> 00:41:18,470
<font color="yellow">Sit down. What would you like?</font>

399
00:41:22,640 --> 00:41:24,900
<font color="yellow">I thought about it, and what do you think about...</font>

400
00:41:25,310 --> 00:41:26,340
<font color="yellow">chicken for dinner?</font>

401
00:41:29,240 --> 00:41:30,700
<font color="yellow">Aren't you craving...</font>

402
00:41:31,400 --> 00:41:32,700
<font color="yellow">chicken for dinner?</font>

403
00:41:33,970 --> 00:41:35,200
<font color="yellow">I guess we have no choice.</font>

404
00:41:35,770 --> 00:41:38,670
<font color="yellow">Tonight's dinner will have to be chicken.</font>

405
00:41:40,270 --> 00:41:41,940
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry for being selfish,</font>

406
00:41:42,400 --> 00:41:43,810
<font color="yellow">but tonight's dinner is...</font>

407
00:41:43,810 --> 00:41:44,970
<font color="yellow">Shut it.</font>

408
00:41:46,970 --> 00:41:50,200
<font color="yellow">Grim Reaper, I need to talk to you.</font>

409
00:41:53,400 --> 00:41:55,870
<font color="yellow">You can start without me. I'll be back before it's cold.</font>

410
00:41:55,870 --> 00:41:57,870
<font color="yellow">I'd rather just die...</font>

411
00:42:04,310 --> 00:42:06,440
<font color="yellow">Why do you keep coming to our store?</font>

412
00:42:06,440 --> 00:42:08,570
<font color="yellow">It can't be because of me.</font>

413
00:42:08,940 --> 00:42:10,810
<font color="yellow">Are you after my boss?</font>

414
00:42:10,810 --> 00:42:11,970
<font color="yellow">It's not like that.</font>

415
00:42:12,240 --> 00:42:13,770
<font color="yellow">I only go there to see her.</font>

416
00:42:14,400 --> 00:42:16,340
<font color="yellow">As long as you keep quiet,</font>

417
00:42:16,640 --> 00:42:18,240
<font color="yellow">everything will be peaceful.</font>

418
00:42:18,240 --> 00:42:19,840
<font color="yellow">It's you who should keep quiet.</font>

419
00:42:19,840 --> 00:42:22,040
<font color="yellow">Don't mention about Tae Hee's visiting me...</font>

420
00:42:22,040 --> 00:42:23,900
<font color="yellow">and that he smiled at me.</font>

421
00:42:23,900 --> 00:42:25,700
<font color="yellow">He also bought two more chickens on his way out.</font>

422
00:42:25,700 --> 00:42:27,270
<font color="yellow">It's our secret.</font>

423
00:42:27,400 --> 00:42:28,470
<font color="yellow">A secret?</font>

424
00:42:30,340 --> 00:42:33,070
<font color="yellow">He came to visit you at work? He smiled at you?</font>

425
00:42:33,070 --> 00:42:35,570
<font color="yellow">Sure, you might want to keep his smile a secret,</font>

426
00:42:35,570 --> 00:42:37,170
<font color="yellow">but why the take out?</font>

