00:44:02,340 --> 00:44:04,140
<font color="yellow">I bet you did well, too.</font>

456
00:44:04,140 --> 00:44:05,340
<font color="yellow">You're really smart.</font>

457
00:44:05,340 --> 00:44:07,100
<font color="yellow">I know you don't get any tutoring.</font>

