00:44:07,540 --> 00:44:08,640
<font color="yellow">That's pretty amazing.</font>

459
00:44:08,640 --> 00:44:10,470
<font color="yellow">- Are you being sarcastic? - No, I mean it.</font>

460
00:44:11,470 --> 00:44:13,140
