497
00:46:46,570 --> 00:46:47,900
<font color="yellow">You should go home.</font>

498
00:46:49,400 --> 00:46:51,070
<font color="yellow">I'll do well on my interview.</font>

499
00:46:51,570 --> 00:46:53,140
<font color="yellow">Thank you for the scarf.</font>

500
00:46:53,140 --> 00:46:54,440
<font color="yellow">Watch out behind you.</font>

501
00:46:55,070 --> 00:46:56,240
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry.</font>

502
00:46:57,240 --> 00:46:58,770
<font color="yellow">I was going to dodge her.</font>

503
00:46:59,070 --> 00:47:02,470
<font color="yellow">Your eyes are so huge and clear that everything reflects on it.</font>

504
00:47:02,470 --> 00:47:04,170
<font color="yellow">All right. Just get on the bus.</font>

505
00:47:19,300 --> 00:47:22,170
<font color="yellow">Thief! It's a pickpocket!</font>

506
00:49:25,800 --> 00:49:26,840
<font color="yellow">Bye.</font>

507
00:49:27,970 --> 00:49:29,070
<font color="yellow">But why?</font>

508
00:49:30,070 --> 00:49:31,600
<font color="yellow">You're not in the scene.</font>

