00:49:31,870 --> 00:49:32,900
<font color="yellow">What's that?</font>

510
00:49:41,070 --> 00:49:43,570
<font color="yellow">My mom will kill me if I fail another interview.</font>

511
00:49:44,440 --> 00:49:46,070
<font color="yellow">I wish I got into a car accident.</font>

512
00:49:46,570 --> 00:49:48,440
<font color="yellow">Don't say that.</font>

513
00:49:48,640 --> 00:49:50,170
<font color="yellow">You should be careful what you wish for.</font>

