00:50:11,100 --> 00:50:12,570
<font color="yellow">I'm so tired.</font>

518
00:50:12,970 --> 00:50:15,040
<font color="yellow">Have some coffee, Sir.</font>

519
00:50:15,700 --> 00:50:18,900
<font color="yellow">I was the one who said I was tired. Why don't you have one for me?</font>

