00:50:24,370 --> 00:50:26,270
<font color="yellow">Everyone says that.</font>

524
00:50:26,370 --> 00:50:27,440
<font color="yellow">It's good that you know.</font>

525
00:50:31,740 --> 00:50:32,900
<font color="yellow">Who are the new faces?</font>

