527
00:50:35,270 --> 00:50:37,000
<font color="yellow">It must be a serious accident.</font>

528
00:50:37,640 --> 00:50:40,270
<font color="yellow">I heard everyone from the support team got five each.</font>

529
00:50:40,270 --> 00:50:41,870
<font color="yellow">You have way more than that.</font>

