00:50:48,570 --> 00:50:50,670
<font color="yellow">Kim Hyun Jeong, age 34.</font>

532
00:50:51,570 --> 00:50:52,600
<font color="yellow">Park Soo Bin.</font>

533
00:50:53,700 --> 00:50:55,800
<font color="yellow">Age two. Death by accident.</font>

534
00:50:56,740 --> 00:50:58,270
<font color="yellow">They must be mother and baby.</font>

