539
00:51:29,540 --> 00:51:31,900
<font color="yellow">What are you talking about?</font>

540
00:51:31,900 --> 00:51:34,340
<font color="yellow">It means I'll buy everything you have.</font>

541
00:51:36,600 --> 00:51:39,930
