00:52:28,990 --> 00:52:29,990
<font color="yellow">You.</font>

546
00:52:30,540 --> 00:52:32,200
<font color="yellow">You're the one from the bus stop.</font>

547
00:52:32,840 --> 00:52:34,470
<font color="yellow">Why do you keep following me?</font>

548
00:52:34,770 --> 00:52:35,900
<font color="yellow">Make a guess.</font>

549
00:52:55,700 --> 00:53:00,070
<font color="yellow">The cash you stole was merely 23 dollars, 32 dollars,</font>

550
00:53:00,850 --> 00:53:02,650
<font color="yellow">10 dollars, and 3 meal coupons.</font>

551
00:53:04,470 --> 00:53:06,700
<font color="yellow">Do you know how many people could've died because of that?</font>

552
00:53:11,470 --> 00:53:12,600
<font color="yellow">What are you?</font>

553
00:53:13,470 --> 00:53:15,270
<font color="yellow">- Are you a cop? - The person you stole from...</font>

