00:53:20,600 --> 00:53:22,670
<font color="yellow">so she works without wearing a cast for three weeks because of you.</font>

557
00:53:22,670 --> 00:53:24,400
<font color="yellow">What on earth are you on about?</font>

558
00:53:25,900 --> 00:53:26,940
<font color="yellow">Does this wallet belong to you?</font>

559
00:53:26,940 --> 00:53:28,570
<font color="yellow">The monthly pay goes into medical expenses.</font>

560
00:53:28,570 --> 00:53:31,170
<font color="yellow">You make her go into shock from the untreated fracture.</font>

