00:53:32,100 --> 00:53:33,700
<font color="yellow">Shut your mouth or you'll regret it.</font>

562
00:53:34,940 --> 00:53:36,440
<font color="yellow">I asked you who you are.</font>

563
00:53:36,440 --> 00:53:38,740
<font color="yellow">It's not to my liking that I have to save someone like you,</font>

