00:53:38,970 --> 00:53:42,000
<font color="yellow">but it'll have to be a side effect from meddling with human lives.</font>

565
00:53:42,240 --> 00:53:44,540
<font color="yellow">But don't think your punishment is over.</font>

566
00:53:46,440 --> 00:53:49,140
<font color="yellow">You will be punished even after your death.</font>

567
00:53:50,370 --> 00:53:51,370
<font color="yellow">However...</font>

568
00:53:51,700 --> 00:53:53,870
<font color="yellow">An eye for an eye and a tooth for a tooth.</font>

569
00:53:55,370 --> 00:53:56,740
<font color="yellow">This is my way of doing things.</font>

570
00:53:58,570 --> 00:53:59,770
<font color="yellow">It'll hurt a little.</font>

571
00:54:00,170 --> 00:54:01,270
<font color="yellow">Bear with it if you'd like.</font>

572
00:54:07,340 --> 00:54:08,370
<font color="yellow">Oh, my hand!</font>

573
00:54:27,340 --> 00:54:29,170
<font color="yellow">Get on stand by. It's time for work soon.</font>

574
00:54:29,170 --> 00:54:30,870
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

575
00:54:31,570 --> 00:54:34,400
<font color="yellow">The bus is approaching.</font>

