00:54:42,870 --> 00:54:44,440
<font color="yellow">It's Mr. Grim Reaper.</font>

577
00:54:50,000 --> 00:54:52,800
<font color="yellow">Did she just look at you?</font>

578
00:54:53,340 --> 00:54:55,840
<font color="yellow">Can she see us right now?</font>

579
00:54:55,840 --> 00:54:58,140
<font color="yellow">There are some who become like that before they die.</font>

580
00:54:58,270 --> 00:55:00,270
<font color="yellow">Poor girl. She's still young.</font>

581
00:55:00,840 --> 00:55:01,970
<font color="yellow">Why is she...</font>

582
00:55:02,740 --> 00:55:04,470
<font color="yellow">Who has a name of Ji Eun Tak on the list?</font>

