00:55:05,000 --> 00:55:06,540
<font color="yellow">Who are you talking about?</font>

584
00:55:09,540 --> 00:55:12,170
<font color="yellow">Wait, you're right. There is an extra person on the bus.</font>

585
00:55:12,170 --> 00:55:13,800
<font color="yellow">I thought everyone died.</font>

586
00:55:13,900 --> 00:55:18,200
<font color="yellow">Hold on. What happens when there's an extra?</font>

587
00:55:18,470 --> 00:55:20,000
<font color="yellow">There isn't going to be an accident today.</font>

588
00:55:20,840 --> 00:55:21,870
<font color="yellow">It's a bust.</font>

589
00:55:22,200 --> 00:55:24,140
<font color="yellow">What? Why?</font>

590
00:55:33,970 --> 00:55:35,370
<font color="yellow">That bus can't go like that.</font>

591
00:55:35,370 --> 00:55:37,440
<font color="yellow">It's not supposed to. It should get in an accident now.</font>

592
00:55:37,470 --> 00:55:38,900
<font color="yellow">Now should be the time.</font>

593
00:55:38,900 --> 00:55:41,900
<font color="yellow">What do we do? Shouldn't we cause one?</font>

594
00:55:45,740 --> 00:55:48,370
<font color="yellow">The bus just left. Nobody died.</font>

595
00:55:48,370 --> 00:55:52,370
<font color="yellow">This has never happened to me in my 300 years of career.</font>

596
00:55:52,740 --> 00:55:54,600
<font color="yellow">What do we do?</font>

597
00:55:55,270 --> 00:55:58,040
<font color="yellow">This is the first time I witnessed the occurrence of missing souls.</font>

598
00:55:58,840 --> 00:56:01,140
<font color="yellow">This has to be a miracle.</font>

599
00:56:01,800 --> 00:56:04,200
<font color="yellow">So miracles do happen.</font>

600
00:56:08,270 --> 00:56:10,270
<font color="yellow">Do you know how much paperwork this miracle is worth of?</font>

601
00:56:10,270 --> 00:56:11,900
<font color="yellow">Watch your mouth.</font>

602
00:56:12,940 --> 00:56:15,100
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry. It's just so astonishing.</font>

603
00:56:15,540 --> 00:56:18,140
<font color="yellow">But how did you know?</font>

604
00:56:25,340 --> 00:56:26,400
<font color="yellow">Oh, gosh.</font>

605
00:56:26,540 --> 00:56:28,800
<font color="yellow">I think it's a goblin.</font>

606
00:56:29,670 --> 00:56:31,470
<font color="yellow">What? Don't I look like one?</font>

607
00:56:33,000 --> 00:56:34,270
<font color="yellow">I need to talk to you.</font>

608
00:56:37,570 --> 00:56:38,670
<font color="yellow">Why didn't you tell me?</font>

609
00:56:38,670 --> 00:56:40,200
<font color="yellow">Why do you keep meddling with human lives?</font>

610
00:56:40,200 --> 00:56:41,570
<font color="yellow">Eun Tak almost died today.</font>

611
00:56:41,570 --> 00:56:43,940
<font color="yellow">If that is her destiny, it can't be avoided.</font>

612
00:56:43,940 --> 00:56:44,970
<font color="yellow">Says who?</font>

613
00:56:46,800 --> 00:56:49,340
<font color="yellow">The only thing I can't grant myself is my own death.</font>

614
00:56:49,940 --> 00:56:53,470
<font color="yellow">Do I have to meddle with every single human life for her?</font>

615
00:56:53,800 --> 00:56:56,370
<font color="yellow">You...That was my workplace.</font>

616
00:56:58,940 --> 00:56:59,970
<font color="yellow">But...</font>

617
00:57:00,800 --> 00:57:02,870
<font color="yellow">No matter how I look at it, today's accident was strange.</font>

618
00:57:04,470 --> 00:57:06,370
<font color="yellow">I foresaw the accident a few days ago,</font>

619
00:57:06,370 --> 00:57:07,970
<font color="yellow">but Eun Tak wasn't there.</font>

620
00:57:07,970 --> 00:57:10,540
<font color="yellow">Besides, I saw her future of 10 years from now.</font>

621
00:57:10,570 --> 00:57:12,840
<font color="yellow">And this accident would've definitely killed her.</font>

622
00:57:12,840 --> 00:57:16,700
<font color="yellow">It's because the accident you foresaw wasn't part of her destiny.</font>

623
00:57:16,970 --> 00:57:20,340
<font color="yellow">She became the variable of the accident.</font>

624
00:57:20,440 --> 00:57:21,740
<font color="yellow">Because you were going to save her.</font>

625
00:57:23,070 --> 00:57:25,400
<font color="yellow">Thanks to the missing soul who has a goblin boyfriend,</font>

626
00:57:25,440 --> 00:57:27,900
<font color="yellow">everyone who was meant to die ended up staying alive.</font>

627
00:57:27,900 --> 00:57:31,100
<font color="yellow">You made me work overtime.</font>

628
00:57:32,540 --> 00:57:34,270
<font color="yellow">Do you want some fried chicken?</font>

629
00:57:34,270 --> 00:57:37,840
<font color="yellow">Will you please consider returning to ashes?</font>

630
00:57:41,740 --> 00:57:45,370
<font color="yellow">It was a joke. No need to take it so seriously.</font>

631
00:57:46,740 --> 00:57:50,470
<font color="yellow">What does it mean to return to ashes?</font>

632
00:57:51,170 --> 00:57:54,670
<font color="yellow">Is it like becoming dust, wind, or rain?</font>

633
00:57:55,140 --> 00:57:56,600
<font color="yellow">And being scattered?</font>

634
00:57:57,670 --> 00:57:59,470
<font color="yellow">Why do you even wonder?</font>

635
00:57:59,600 --> 00:58:02,240
