00:58:05,670 --> 00:58:08,300
<font color="yellow">It even moved, so I...</font>

638
00:58:09,970 --> 00:58:11,700
<font color="yellow">I almost killed her.</font>

639
00:58:15,270 --> 00:58:17,000
<font color="yellow">It hurt so much.</font>

640
00:58:19,800 --> 00:58:21,400
<font color="yellow">I'd never felt so much pain before.</font>

641
00:58:21,540 --> 00:58:25,170
<font color="yellow">Don't you think you should tell her the truth?</font>

642
00:58:26,270 --> 00:58:28,600
<font color="yellow">- About what will happen? - No.</font>

643
00:58:30,670 --> 00:58:32,640
<font color="yellow">I want to hide it if possible.</font>

644
00:58:33,400 --> 00:58:35,270
<font color="yellow">For about 80 more years.</font>

645
00:58:39,770 --> 00:58:42,470
<font color="yellow">- What? - That's a human's lifespan.</font>

646
00:58:42,870 --> 00:58:46,470
<font color="yellow">It's the maximum age a 19-year-old girl can live to be.</font>

647
00:58:46,470 --> 00:58:48,040
<font color="yellow">I want to keep it from her.</font>

648
00:58:49,700 --> 00:58:51,140
<font color="yellow">But can I?</font>

649
00:58:54,300 --> 00:58:55,600
<font color="yellow">No?</font>

650
00:59:09,440 --> 00:59:10,770
<font color="yellow">(Communication Sciences)</font>

651
00:59:27,900 --> 00:59:30,800
<font color="yellow">Did you come to pick me up? What a surprise.</font>

652
00:59:30,800 --> 00:59:32,900
<font color="yellow">I'm out because I felt a little stuffy.</font>

653
00:59:33,970 --> 00:59:37,770
<font color="yellow">I know. There's no way you'd care about my welfare.</font>

654
00:59:42,470 --> 00:59:43,870
<font color="yellow">What's all this?</font>

655
00:59:46,540 --> 00:59:47,670
<font color="yellow">Socks?</font>

656
00:59:47,970 --> 00:59:51,400
<font color="yellow">It signifies the next 10, 20 years of someone I saved today.</font>

657
00:59:56,740 --> 00:59:59,300
<font color="yellow">Did you decide to sell socks...</font>

658
00:59:59,300 --> 01:00:01,640
<font color="yellow">to support me for the next 10, 20 years?</font>

659
01:00:02,140 --> 01:00:03,940
<font color="yellow">Because I asked why you don't work?</font>

660
01:00:06,600 --> 01:00:08,800
<font color="yellow">- Do you want to help out? - Sure.</font>

661
01:00:09,200 --> 01:00:12,340
<font color="yellow">My interviews are over so I'm free now.</font>

662
01:00:12,340 --> 01:00:14,140
<font color="yellow">I'll take better care of you from now on.</font>

663
01:00:14,200 --> 01:00:15,540
<font color="yellow">How do you mean?</font>

664
01:00:24,870 --> 01:00:25,970
<font color="yellow">What are you doing?</font>

665
01:00:27,940 --> 01:00:29,200
<font color="yellow">Exercising.</font>

666
01:00:29,200 --> 01:00:31,800
<font color="yellow">To make sure I pull out the sword in one go next time.</font>

667
01:00:31,800 --> 01:00:35,970
<font color="yellow">I realized last time that I need strong arms for the job.</font>

668
01:00:40,340 --> 01:00:41,700
<font color="yellow">Don't overdo it.</font>

669
01:00:43,840 --> 01:00:46,900
<font color="yellow">Why do you sound so reluctant?</font>

670
01:00:55,070 --> 01:00:58,200
<font color="yellow">Can you excuse me? I need to talk to someone.</font>

671
01:01:00,870 --> 01:01:03,900
<font color="yellow">- To whom? - I won't be long. Go inside.</font>

672
01:01:16,700 --> 01:01:19,370
<font color="yellow">Come over here. Come down to my level.</font>

673
01:01:19,370 --> 01:01:21,940
<font color="yellow">Don't you think you punished me enough?</font>

674
01:01:22,840 --> 01:01:25,940
<font color="yellow">Did you hate the idea of my enjoying something that much?</font>

675
01:01:26,770 --> 01:01:29,970
<font color="yellow">Did you show me that in advance to stop me from doing something?</font>

676
01:01:33,270 --> 01:01:35,670
<font color="yellow">Do you think I'll make that decision?</font>

677
01:01:35,700 --> 01:01:38,170
<font color="yellow">I won't. Never.</font>

678
01:01:38,600 --> 01:01:40,570
<font color="yellow">Come down here.</font>

679
01:01:40,570 --> 01:01:43,770
<font color="yellow">Let's talk face-to-face. Why won't you?</font>

680
01:01:46,040 --> 01:01:48,100
<font color="yellow">Do you think I'm afraid of you? Come down.</font>

681
01:01:48,740 --> 01:01:50,800
<font color="yellow">Why don't you ever face me?</font>

682
01:01:52,340 --> 01:01:54,200
<font color="yellow">Is he still sick?</font>

683
01:02:08,200 --> 01:02:10,970
<font color="yellow">I didn't look. I swear.</font>

684
01:02:11,100 --> 01:02:12,970
<font color="yellow">I really don't like this.</font>

685
01:02:14,840 --> 01:02:16,370
<font color="yellow">Having to like you...</font>

686
01:02:18,200 --> 01:02:20,470
<font color="yellow">I couldn't be more foolish.</font>

687
01:02:23,670 --> 01:02:24,870
<font color="yellow">What...</font>

688
01:02:26,270 --> 01:02:28,400
<font color="yellow">did you just say to me?</font>

689
01:02:28,400 --> 01:02:30,240
<font color="yellow">- It's fine if you missed it. - I heard everything.</font>

690
01:02:30,240 --> 01:02:31,470
<font color="yellow">Then good.</font>

691
01:02:48,840 --> 01:02:51,140
<font color="yellow">Does that mean...</font>

692
01:02:52,040 --> 01:02:55,970
<font color="yellow">he actually confessed his love for me?</font>

693
01:02:56,540 --> 01:02:59,400
<font color="yellow">What's wrong with him?</font>

694
01:03:26,100 --> 01:03:28,500
<font color="yellow">48.</font>

695
01:03:29,970 --> 01:03:32,630
<font color="yellow">49.</font>

696
01:03:34,000 --> 01:03:36,200
<font color="yellow">50.</font>

697
01:03:48,970 --> 01:03:51,300
<font color="yellow">(10 missed calls)</font>

698
01:03:57,170 --> 01:04:00,500
<font color="yellow">You never call so I didn't bother to check my phone.</font>

699
01:04:00,500 --> 01:04:02,400
<font color="yellow">You startled me.</font>

700
01:04:08,660 --> 01:04:10,690
<font color="yellow">I was surprised that you called me first.</font>

701
01:04:11,630 --> 01:04:13,360
<font color="yellow">10 missed calls?</font>

702
01:04:14,030 --> 01:04:16,790
<font color="yellow">I was working late when I thought of something to say.</font>

703
01:04:17,660 --> 01:04:19,690
<font color="yellow">It must've been really important.</font>

704
01:04:21,030 --> 01:04:22,060
<font color="yellow">It is.</font>

705
01:04:24,430 --> 01:04:27,160
<font color="yellow">I don't have a religion.</font>

706
01:04:29,690 --> 01:04:32,860
<font color="yellow">You speak so well. Do you have a religion?</font>

707
01:04:32,930 --> 01:04:36,030
<font color="yellow">Do I need to have something else again?</font>

708
01:04:36,190 --> 01:04:38,260
<font color="yellow">I'll call you when I have it.</font>

709
01:04:39,360 --> 01:04:42,660
<font color="yellow">Did you call me 10 times just to tell me that?</font>

710
01:04:42,660 --> 01:04:44,930
<font color="yellow">I thought I should tell you as soon as possible.</font>

711
01:04:48,460 --> 01:04:49,690
<font color="yellow">You're cute.</font>

712
01:04:50,490 --> 01:04:51,660
<font color="yellow">Am I...</font>

713
01:04:52,290 --> 01:04:54,230
<font color="yellow">- cute? - Didn't you know?</font>

714
01:04:54,760 --> 01:04:57,260
<font color="yellow">Didn't any of the other women tell you so?</font>

715
01:04:59,260 --> 01:05:01,630
<font color="yellow">I didn't have any other women...</font>

716
01:05:01,630 --> 01:05:04,190
<font color="yellow">That's a good thing. Not having other women.</font>

717
01:05:04,230 --> 01:05:06,030
<font color="yellow">Don't go looking for any.</font>

718
01:05:06,930 --> 01:05:09,730
<font color="yellow">You're perfect as you are, okay?</font>

719
01:05:14,090 --> 01:05:15,890
<font color="yellow">Is he a player?</font>

720
01:05:18,330 --> 01:05:21,390
<font color="yellow">Tell me this and be very honest.</font>

721
01:05:21,790 --> 01:05:23,290
<font color="yellow">I will tell you, too.</font>

722
01:05:24,030 --> 01:05:25,090
<font color="yellow">Tell me what?</font>

723
01:05:25,090 --> 01:05:27,290
<font color="yellow">My real first name has only one syllable.</font>

724
01:05:28,230 --> 01:05:30,090
<font color="yellow">Kim Sun.</font>

725
01:05:34,660 --> 01:05:36,360
<font color="yellow">My parents were poor,</font>

726
01:05:36,860 --> 01:05:38,930
<font color="yellow">but they still paid someone...</font>

727
01:05:38,930 --> 01:05:41,030
<font color="yellow">to come up with a good name.</font>

728
01:05:41,330 --> 01:05:44,430
<font color="yellow">The fortune-teller said I had to have this name.</font>

729
01:05:44,690 --> 01:05:47,090
<font color="yellow">But I prefer Sunny.</font>

730
01:05:47,230 --> 01:05:49,560
<font color="yellow">I think I shine brighter when I'm Sunny.</font>

731
01:05:50,960 --> 01:05:53,260
<font color="yellow">I really hated that name.</font>

732
01:05:54,230 --> 01:05:57,230
<font color="yellow">It sounds sad like something happened in the past.</font>

733
01:05:58,230 --> 01:05:59,430
<font color="yellow">Kim Sun.</font>

734
01:06:05,560 --> 01:06:07,260
<font color="yellow">Our master...</font>

735
01:06:08,290 --> 01:06:11,560
<font color="yellow">goes there around this time every year...</font>

736
01:06:11,960 --> 01:06:13,890
<font color="yellow">and launches a sky lantern.</font>

737
01:06:15,790 --> 01:06:17,260
<font color="yellow">Woo Bin.</font>

738
01:06:18,460 --> 01:06:20,560
<font color="yellow">What's your real name?</font>

739
01:06:23,160 --> 01:06:24,990
<font color="yellow">I know your name is fake.</font>

740
01:06:25,290 --> 01:06:27,560
<font color="yellow">Even if it's weird or doesn't suit you,</font>

741
01:06:27,560 --> 01:06:31,090
<font color="yellow">I won't tease you, so can't you tell me?</font>

742
01:07:21,660 --> 01:07:25,030
<font color="yellow">I give you the sword with rage and concern.</font>

743
01:07:28,130 --> 01:07:30,990
<font color="yellow">Go as far as you can, as if possible,</font>

744
01:07:31,230 --> 01:07:32,630
<font color="yellow">do not return.</font>

745
01:07:33,960 --> 01:07:35,530
<font color="yellow">Your Majesty, do you mean...</font>

746
01:07:37,130 --> 01:07:38,790
<font color="yellow">How could you...</font>

747
01:07:39,060 --> 01:07:40,760
<font color="yellow">Goryeo is your nation.</font>

748
01:07:42,890 --> 01:07:45,790
<font color="yellow">You ordered me to guard the border, so I did.</font>

749
01:07:46,530 --> 01:07:49,090
<font color="yellow">You ordered me to kill the enemy, so I did.</font>

750
01:07:50,430 --> 01:07:52,460
<font color="yellow">My sister is here and so are the people...</font>

751
01:07:52,460 --> 01:07:53,930
<font color="yellow">You now understand...</font>

752
01:07:55,790 --> 01:07:57,490
<font color="yellow">the concerns of the King.</font>

753
01:07:59,490 --> 01:08:01,430
<font color="yellow">Notify me of your death,</font>

754
01:08:01,790 --> 01:08:03,830
<font color="yellow">and I shall notify you of my sorrow.</font>

755
01:08:06,660 --> 01:08:07,790
<font color="yellow">It is my royal decree.</font>

756
01:08:47,200 --> 01:08:49,130
<font color="yellow">Is something wrong?</font>

757
01:09:02,430 --> 01:09:05,030
<font color="yellow">Is it your chest? Your stomach? What did you eat for dinner?</font>

758
01:09:05,030 --> 01:09:07,060
<font color="yellow">Are your hands cold? Give me your hand.</font>

759
01:09:07,060 --> 01:09:09,290
<font color="yellow">If you massage your hand, it'll help blood flow and...</font>

760
01:09:13,630 --> 01:09:14,890
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry,</font>

761
01:09:15,700 --> 01:09:17,560
<font color="yellow">but please look into my eyes.</font>

762
01:09:18,360 --> 01:09:19,360
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

763
01:09:20,460 --> 01:09:23,530
<font color="yellow">You did not see me today.</font>

764
01:09:23,990 --> 01:09:25,890
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry I can't take you home.</font>

765
01:09:26,700 --> 01:09:28,390
<font color="yellow">Turn around and go home.</font>

766
01:10:00,630 --> 01:10:02,530
<font color="yellow">Where did he go?</font>

767
01:10:03,560 --> 01:10:04,790
<font color="yellow">From now on,</font>

768
01:10:05,890 --> 01:10:08,560
<font color="yellow">you'll have to serve Master Kim,</font>

769
01:10:08,730 --> 01:10:12,290
<font color="yellow">so you must remember this day clearly.</font>

770
01:10:12,290 --> 01:10:13,790
<font color="yellow">Why is he launching lanterns?</font>

771
01:10:14,360 --> 01:10:15,430
<font color="yellow">Who are they?</font>

772
01:10:15,430 --> 01:10:16,830
<font color="yellow">They are people...</font>

773
01:10:17,960 --> 01:10:21,700
<font color="yellow">to whom he owed a debt in his heart for a very long time.</font>

774
01:10:23,960 --> 01:10:28,460
<font color="yellow">I heard there is a sword stuck in Uncle's chest. Do you know about it?</font>

775
01:10:28,460 --> 01:10:30,160
<font color="yellow">How did you know that?</font>

776
01:10:30,430 --> 01:10:35,230
<font color="yellow">You cannot let our master know that you know about it.</font>

777
01:10:35,330 --> 01:10:36,330
<font color="yellow">Why not?</font>

778
01:10:57,660 --> 01:10:59,160
<font color="yellow">That sword...</font>

779
01:11:00,200 --> 01:11:02,930
<font color="yellow">is his prize and punishment.</font>

780
01:11:04,330 --> 01:11:07,390
<font color="yellow">It is his reason for existing,</font>

781
01:11:07,390 --> 01:11:09,930
<font color="yellow">and the clue to his extinction.</font>

782
01:11:33,030 --> 01:11:34,430
<font color="yellow">You are my life...</font>

783
01:11:36,290 --> 01:11:37,990
<font color="yellow">and my death.</font>

784
01:11:41,030 --> 01:11:42,030
<font color="yellow">And I...</font>

785
01:11:42,890 --> 01:11:44,160
<font color="yellow">like you.</font>

786
01:11:46,390 --> 01:11:48,330
<font color="yellow">Thus, I keep this secret...</font>

787
01:11:51,130 --> 01:11:53,260
<font color="yellow">and ask above for permission.</font>

788
01:11:55,290 --> 01:11:57,160
<font color="yellow">May you not know for one more day.</font>

789
01:11:58,290 --> 01:12:00,560
<font color="yellow">May you not know for 100 years more.</font>

790
01:12:48,290 --> 01:12:49,490
<font color="yellow">You know me, right?</font>

791
01:12:51,230 --> 01:12:52,700
<font color="yellow">I need to talk to you.</font>

792
01:12:53,390 --> 01:12:54,700
<font color="yellow">Do you have time?</font>

793
01:12:55,660 --> 01:12:57,360
<font color="yellow">Will you please get right to it?</font>

794
01:12:58,360 --> 01:13:01,730
<font color="yellow">I don't feel like speaking with a deity right now.</font>

795
01:13:07,660 --> 01:13:09,560
<font color="yellow">Something went wrong.</font>

796
01:13:13,530 --> 01:13:14,560
<font color="yellow">I think...</font>

797
01:13:15,560 --> 01:13:17,660
<font color="yellow">it starts with you.</font>

798
01:13:27,160 --> 01:13:29,090
<font color="yellow">Where did he go?</font>

799
01:13:30,790 --> 01:13:32,030
<font color="yellow">This is why...</font>

800
01:13:32,560 --> 01:13:34,490
<font color="yellow">I said even if he doesn't say he's coming,</font>

801
01:13:34,490 --> 01:13:37,030
<font color="yellow">I want him to say if he's leaving.</font>

802
01:13:41,960 --> 01:13:43,390
<font color="yellow">What do you want to know?</font>

803
01:13:46,700 --> 01:13:48,130
<font color="yellow">Well, so...</font>

804
01:13:51,130 --> 01:13:52,760
<font color="yellow">I told you before.</font>

805
01:13:52,760 --> 01:13:55,630
<font color="yellow">Once my bride appears, I must prepare to go farther away.</font>

806
01:13:56,890 --> 01:13:59,660
<font color="yellow">Something seemed strange.</font>

807
01:13:59,990 --> 01:14:02,430
<font color="yellow">You know the sword in the goblin's chest.</font>

808
01:14:03,290 --> 01:14:06,390
<font color="yellow">What happens exactly...</font>

809
01:14:06,760 --> 01:14:08,430
<font color="yellow">if I remove it?</font>

810
01:14:09,560 --> 01:14:11,560
<font color="yellow">He kept saying he's going somewhere.</font>

811
01:14:11,560 --> 01:14:13,660
<font color="yellow">Does that mean you're not leaving?</font>

812
01:14:13,660 --> 01:14:14,760
<font color="yellow">For now.</font>

813
01:14:16,260 --> 01:14:19,030
<font color="yellow">I may have to prepare to go farther away.</font>

814
01:14:19,290 --> 01:14:20,630
<font color="yellow">Where is that?</font>

815
01:14:30,330 --> 01:14:32,260
<font color="yellow">Remove that sword quickly.</font>

816
01:14:33,430 --> 01:14:36,430
<font color="yellow">Remove the sword and return to ashes.</font>

817
01:14:38,790 --> 01:14:41,990
<font color="yellow">You show up out of the blue and tell me to die.</font>

818
01:14:43,430 --> 01:14:45,160
<font color="yellow">Shouldn't you tell me why...</font>

819
01:14:45,160 --> 01:14:47,030
<font color="yellow">You've lived long enough,</font>

820
01:14:47,760 --> 01:14:49,530
<font color="yellow">but not her.</font>

821
01:14:50,290 --> 01:14:53,700
<font color="yellow">I was truly happy when I created her,</font>

822
01:14:54,130 --> 01:14:55,730
<font color="yellow">so decide now.</font>

823
01:15:00,090 --> 01:15:01,430
<font color="yellow">How ironic.</font>

824
01:15:02,830 --> 01:15:05,790
<font color="yellow">I don't know what decision you want me to make.</font>

825
01:15:07,390 --> 01:15:09,790
<font color="yellow">When I was first born as Kim Shin,</font>

826
01:15:09,790 --> 01:15:11,760
<font color="yellow">you must have created me.</font>

827
01:15:13,230 --> 01:15:14,730
<font color="yellow">Am I not your child?</font>

828
01:15:14,730 --> 01:15:16,890
<font color="yellow">That's why I'm telling you.</font>

829
01:15:16,890 --> 01:15:20,090
<font color="yellow">For my child, Kim Shin, for whom I wished happiness.</font>

830
01:15:21,390 --> 01:15:23,760
<font color="yellow">Because it is what you want the most.</font>

831
01:15:25,200 --> 01:15:28,090
<font color="yellow">- What do I want? - You want her to live.</font>

832
01:15:28,090 --> 01:15:30,030
<font color="yellow">If you don't return to ashes,</font>

833
01:15:30,200 --> 01:15:31,700
<font color="yellow">Eun Tak will die.</font>

834
01:15:34,660 --> 01:15:35,890
<font color="yellow">So...</font>

835
01:15:38,790 --> 01:15:40,430
<font color="yellow">he wanted to die.</font>

836
01:15:42,090 --> 01:15:44,060
<font color="yellow">That's why he wanted me to be his bride...</font>

837
01:15:45,230 --> 01:15:47,560
<font color="yellow">and remove that sword?</font>

838
01:15:54,030 --> 01:15:55,130
<font color="yellow">So...</font>

839
01:15:57,660 --> 01:15:59,390
<font color="yellow">if I remove that sword,</font>

840
01:16:01,630 --> 01:16:03,960
<font color="yellow">he will die?</font>

841
01:16:08,390 --> 01:16:09,560
<font color="yellow">So...</font>

842
01:16:13,760 --> 01:16:15,330
<font color="yellow">if I remove that sword,</font>

843
01:16:17,830 --> 01:16:20,060
<font color="yellow">he will disappear...</font>

844
01:16:20,990 --> 01:16:23,230
<font color="yellow">from this world? For good?</font>

845
01:16:35,990 --> 01:16:38,360
<font color="yellow">She was born to pull out your sword. That's her fate.</font>

846
01:16:38,390 --> 01:16:41,160
<font color="yellow">No, you gave her that fate.</font>

847
01:16:46,200 --> 01:16:49,460
<font color="yellow">She'll become useless if she doesn't do what she was born to do.</font>

848
01:16:49,460 --> 01:16:51,430
<font color="yellow">There will be no reason for her existence.</font>

849
01:16:52,760 --> 01:16:54,460
